dlentry.dd:
Checks in the selected document on the server. This action opens theCheck
            In dialog. In this dialog, the following options are available:

Minor Version - increments the minor version of the file on
              the server;

Major Version - increments the major version of the file on
              the server;

Overwrite - overwrites the latest version of the file on the
              server;

Comment - allows you to comment on a file that you check
              in.
